    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You utilize your physiology to its fullest, ejecting Chakra strings from your back unit to pull yourself away from oncoming danger.</p><p>Target a surface within range. You extend Chakra strings toward it, embedding them inside, and retract, pulling yourself towards it at high speeds. Attacks of opportunity made during this movement are made at disadvantage.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and its range by 10 feet. When casting this jutsu at B-Rank or higher, it can be cast as a reaction.</p>",
